{
  "texts": [
    "• Prompting (Generating Nonsensical Statements): Next, to generate nonsensical statements, we rephrased the questions into declarative sentences.",
    "Taking the example from the left part of Fig. 3, which illustrates a question from the CommonsenseQA dataset along with its answer choices, we first excluded the correct answer (\"write down\").",
    "Then, the question and the remaining incorrect options were input into GPT-4.",
    "The model was asked to select the least implausible choice and rephrase the question as a declarative statement incorporating that incorrect choice.",
    "In this specific example, GPT-4 selected \"talk\" as the least implausible option and generated the statement: \"You would express information to a deaf person by talking.\""
  ]
}